Stay Safe Online Checklist:
 •	Never share your OTP, passwords, or UPI PIN with anyone 
 •	Do not click on unknown or suspicious links 
 •	Always verify the identity of callers claiming to be from banks or companies 
 •	Use strong and unique passwords for all accounts 
 •	Enable two-factor authentication wherever possible 
 •	Avoid using public Wi-Fi for financial transactions 
UPI / Financial Safety:
 •	Never enter your UPI PIN to receive money 
 •	Always check payment requests carefully before approving 
Reporting:
 •	Report cyber fraud at: cybercrime.gov.in 
 •	Call helpline: 1930

